
This posting is the complete, unabridged Battleship game with all sorts
of bug fixes and new features.

	o It is truly random now.
	o It checks LOGNAME to find who you are.
	o You can edit your coordinates.
	o You can optionally see the computer players misses.
	o You can optionally have the computer look at your board to see
	  whether it hits or misses
	o You can play the legal way, or in Blitz mode.
	o It is now compatible with both System V and BSD Unix.
	o The computer strategy has been changed somewhat.

This should be the definitive version.

